  "interop_compat_risks": "While this is a behavioral change, in that the user action pseudos will no longer match across top layer boundaries, it is very unlikely to cause compat issues, because the old behavior was so broken. It is unlikely that a site is relying on that behavior intentionally. While it's possible they unintentionally did so, but in that case, this feature will effectively be a bug fix for those sites.",
